<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>8+N一键烹饪，智享美好食光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200918/516fcca4db894cb4a3bab56735ff9c5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
